{"tid":918490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）明治天皇登機同一年，越南曾想革國音漢字，香港獨立後可以作為參考","createTime":"2018-11-27T09:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T12:43:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79d0f277c2f38bf26efb91f530ef1edef60aa694","tid":918490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6982030&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6982030%26page%3D1&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6d6b9daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6982030&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先睇下你哋見過呢啲字未<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/QoxFYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FQoxFYH.jpg&h=53b4b8dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/gT2CJw.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FgT2CJw.jpeg&h=b8a1addc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/BKp6Ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FBKp6Ah.jpg&h=e3aa74ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/qSFMp9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FqSFMp9.png&h=4020bea8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/V2mTEc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FV2mTEc.jpg&h=9e01135e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/W2GJlw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FW2GJlw.jpg&h=c860a7fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n其實越南喺法國占領前，一直有用漢字，但係佢哋發展出自己一套獨有嘅漢字系統，叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喃字</span></span>，寫法我地中國人應唔多睇得明，但造字方式係一樣 。 1867年，越南阮朝改革志士阮長祚提議將喃字標準化（並連同廢除文言文），改成「國音漢字」，可惜嗣德皇帝唔制，到1949年俾PK越共廢埋，變咗呢啲拉丁化低等民族純標音文。"},{"pid":"7db3a0c8a6db0b0e3f65c6c9d60510913899a7dc","tid":918490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/XTP5u6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FXTP5u6.jpg&h=4da48223&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/QP8dtw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FQP8dtw.jpg&h=87baff8f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/hHVRM9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FhHVRM9.jpg&h=d4886a5d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/GY2NQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FGY2NQR.jpg&h=cdd1dc5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/Y5avxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FY5avxU.jpg&h=108713b1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/UWCoeP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FUWCoeP.jpg&h=5e706fab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/PsphjZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FPsphjZ.jpg&h=4545d942&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/Dn7X3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FDn7X3T.jpg&h=ffb79257&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/lbvrUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FlbvrUE.jpg&h=c311dbe3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/vL2kWf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FvL2kWf.jpg&h=586c9e85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/08/QoDcU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2FQoDcU2.jpg&h=0314d7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一/壹</span></span>字變咗<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒</span></span>字，真係好奇怪"},{"pid":"7fc7814862b2841f0af790ab284a1a5067b7ebc2","tid":918490,"uid":127032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:21:39.000Z","msg":"好似d電腦亂打嘅字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eea89debc34975fdf0fd7237db7da54b117727e","tid":918490,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:30:52.000Z","msg":"亂碼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前去越南西貢，想睇下有無博物館有無收藏呢啲字嘅古籍，但搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得文言文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a387ca7ed9ed10794c43ba4d6f08d30599ca51c5","tid":918490,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"一個字義(中文)加字音"},{"pid":"533451088349fd6d03b006738160bf9baf445fe2","tid":918490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a387ca7ed9ed10794c43ba4d6f08d30599ca51c5","tid":918490,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"一個字義(中文)加字音"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"漢字同中文係兩樣野嚟，咪撈亂"},{"pid":"fd8efd7911861f0fe9029304b6258b35b33667be","tid":918490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}